# TQM data caches — reproducible, kept off git to keep the repo small.
# data/raw/ holds NVR pulls (*.mp4 already gitignored above).
# data/sessions/ is the per-session video cache (combined + trimmed +
# boundaries) built by pipeline.session_video. Each session is ~1.5 GB
# on disk — recomputable from raw + boundary detection. Should have
# been gitignored alongside the others below in step 9.
# data/evidence_cache/ is rebuilt by pipeline.evidence (each cached bundle
# can be ~1MB; sweeping many sessions would bloat the repo fast).
# data/rubric_runs/ is per-run output keyed on config — useful locally,
# recomputable from cache + script.
data/sessions/
data/evidence_cache/
data/rubric_runs/
data/_answer_queue/

# Migration audit log — append-only on disk, derivable from migrate_*
# scripts. Tracked across machines via the scripts themselves.
migration_log.txt
data/tqm_answers.backup_*.xlsx
